rdebootstrap (0.1.16) unstable; urgency=medium

  * change: do not stage apt-lists by default to avoid updates when mirror 
    indexes drift.
  * feat: --snapshot today. Using "now" is problematic because Debian and 
    Ubuntu snapshot services are eventually consistent; index files downloaded 
    at "now" may later drift.
  * fix: add more comprehensive unit tests to improve coverage and robustness

 -- Alexey Naidyonov <alexey.naidyonov@gmail.com>  Sat, 28 Mar 2026 19:52:10 +0000

