rdebootstrap (0.1.13) unstable; urgency=medium

  * fix: Store imported-universe hash in Manifest::set_import.
  * feat: Import command now accepts --import <other-manifest.toml>
    instead of an archive definition or a distro template.
  * feat: Commands that accept relative paths (deb, artifact, import)
    now resolve those paths relative to the target manifest file.

